{"tid":2237763,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周庭30萬日文Q&A","createTime":"2020-10-10T14:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T15:19:19.000Z","uid":229510,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f63ee01534d93ad69d49b75e709335da453e923d","tid":2237763,"uid":229510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"首播中<br />\n<br />\n每日推周庭姐姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毋懼國安法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到超越大J成為香港第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐今日有一段新片<br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐最新影片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/53_ASnqWVt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F53_ASnqWVt8&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f0be95e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/53_ASnqWVt8</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐YouTube&nbsp;channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=978200fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes%3Fs%3D09&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3314b2eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐Instagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=5cdf3b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐Facebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fagneschowting&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2bd6d65d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周庭姐姐 宇宙最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nユーチューブの中国検閲者は新型コロナウイルスに関する動画に黄色アイコンが付いてました、黄色アイコン付いてる動画がアド出るのこと難しいになる<br />\n<br />\nこれは香港だけの悩みではなく、日本ユーチューバーが黄色アイコンでマークされるの可能性も高い、だから香港人と共に、ユーチューブに圧力をかけてください<br />\n<br />\nこのポストは周庭お姉さんが香港一のユーチゥーバーなりるまでに、毎日周庭お姉さんのこと押します<br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん今日新しい動画が一本あります<br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん最新動画:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/53_ASnqWVt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F53_ASnqWVt8&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f0be95e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/53_ASnqWVt8</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さんユーチューブ&nbsp;チャンネル:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=978200fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さんツイッター:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes%3Fs%3D09&d=qh